data.description: This updated split level is nestled in the lush, desirable Burlingame neighborhood on a quiet cul-de-sac. This home offers a large living room with lots of natural light, brand new carpeting and flooring. The open kitchen and dining room concept with a slider that connects to a large 35x20 deck and fenced yard, is great for entertaining. Enjoy the large garage w/built-ins and plenty of storage. The 4th bedroom downstairs is perfect for guest quarters or a den area. Separate entrance for side office. Sought after location to freeways, shops, restaurants w/easy access to Lake Oswego, Multnomah Village & OHSU. Short distance to 645 acre Tryon Creek State Park!
